/* --------------------- REXX ------------------------ *
 | REXX code to drive the demonstration of Field Level |
 | Help in an ISPF Panel                               |
 | ISPF - Developers - Tips and Tricks                 |
 * --------------------------------------------------- */
  Address ISPExec
  do forever
    'Display Panel(PNFLDH)'
    if rc > 0 then leave
  end
